---
title: Pork Satay Skewers with Turmeric Rice
description: These mouthwatering fusion kebabs are finger-licking great and quick and easy to make. Cubes of tender pork loin marinated in warm spices threaded onto skewers and served on a bed on fragrant vegetable rice. Don’t forget the crowning glory - a delicious peanut and lime satay sauce drizzled on top. Divine!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-satay-skewers-36039dbc-a50c97bc.jpg
